 will showcase the new additions, alongside the details for the upcoming Achilles Event.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We plan to make the changes live to all players on 1.41 shortly after the blog post is published. The SPPs will also be provided with all the new 5* relics at the same time.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>SOLO WAR &#8211; <em>Tengu: The Forged Tanto<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"812\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/Tengu_square-1024x812.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1252\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/Tengu_square-1024x812.png 1024w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/Tengu_square-300x238.png 300w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/Tengu_square-768x609.png 768w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/Tengu_square-1536x1217.png 1536w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/Tengu_square.png 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>STARTS:<\/strong> 12th April, 14:00 UTC<br><strong>ENDS:<\/strong> 15th April, 10:00 UTC<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tengu, the restless spirit, returns to battle with newfound prowess. Witness the power of his new <strong>Prestige Skill<\/strong> and the new <strong>Synergy<\/strong> effect from the <strong><em>TANTO BLADE<\/em><\/strong><em> <\/em>relic<em>. <\/em>When equipped, Tengu\u2019s troops deal more damage and his fifth skill will react to enemy spell casts and summons.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"842\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/tengu